modName: Offical Thieves Guild Bounty Clearer - Audio Remaster
summary: The mod Thieves Guild Bounty Clearer is a mod adds a unique fully voiced Thieves Guild NPC to their underground hideout. This NPC if you befriend the Thieves Guild will use his connections throughout Skyrim to remove bounties on your head at half the price. This mod adds HD quality audio to the original mod "Thieves Guild Bounty Clearer.
author: Edmond Noir
